[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "Mr Jones during this interval attempted once or twice to speak, but was absolutely incapable, muttering only, or rather sighing out, some broken words; when Sophia at length, partly out of pity to him, and partly to turn the discourse from the subject which she knew well enough he was endeavouring to open, said-",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "Justice I know must condemn me.--Yet not for the letter I sent to Lady Bellaston.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000009_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000009_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "Indeed, you have acted strangely.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000009_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000009_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "Think, most adorable creature, of my unhappy situation, of my despair.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000009_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000009_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "No repentance was ever more sincere.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000009_000018",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000009_000018.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "You must expect, however, that if I can be prevailed on by your repentance to pardon you, I will at least insist on the strongest proof of its sincerity.\" \"Name any proof in my power,\" answered Jones eagerly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000009_000019",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000009_000019.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "\"Time,\" replied she; \"time alone, Mr Jones, can convince me that you are a true penitent, and have resolved to abandon these vicious courses, which I should detest you for, if I imagined you capable of persevering in them.\" \"Do not imagine it,\" cries Jones.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000009_000020",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000009_000020.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "\"On my knees I intreat, I implore your confidence, a confidence which it shall be the business of my life to deserve.\" \"Let it then,\" said she, \"be the business of some part of your life to shew me you deserve it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000009_000021",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000009_000021.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "I think I have been explicit enough in assuring you, that, when I see you merit my confidence, you will obtain it. After what is past, sir, can you expect I should take you upon your word?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "\"What is that?\" said Sophia, a little surprized.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000010_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000010_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "Impossible! my Sophia; they would fix a Dorimant, a Lord Rochester.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000010_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000010_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "The first moment of hope that my Sophia might be my wife taught it me at once; and all the rest of her sex from that moment became as little the objects of desire to my sense as of passion to my heart.\" \"Well,\" says Sophia, \"the proof of this must be from time.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000010_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000010_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "I will not dare to press anything further than you permit me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000010_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000010_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "Nay, I will not.\"--\"O! don't look unkindly thus, my Sophia,\" cries he.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000010_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000010_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "\"I do not, I dare not press you.--Yet permit me at least once more to beg you would fix the period.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000010_000016",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000010_000016.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "\"O! my Sophia,\" cries he, \"you have named an eternity.\"--\"Perhaps it may be something sooner,\" says she; \"I will not be teazed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "At this instant Western, who had stood some time listening, burst into the room, and, with his hunting voice and phrase, cried out, \"To her, boy, to her, go to her.----That's it, little honeys, O that's it! Well! what, is it all over?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000011_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000011_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "Come, confess, and be an honest girl for once.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000011_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000011_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "What, art dumb?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000011_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000011_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "Why dost not speak?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000011_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000011_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "All the spirit of contrary, that's all.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "Dost repent heartily of thy promise, dost not, Sophia?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "In which the history is concluded.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "There likewise he met his uncle, who was returned to town in quest of his new married daughter.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "This marriage was the luckiest incident which could have happened to the young gentleman; for these brothers lived in a constant state of contention about the government of their children, both heartily despising the method which each other took.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "As for the other, who really loved his daughter with the most immoderate affection, there was little difficulty in inclining him to a reconciliation.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "He was no sooner informed by his nephew where his daughter and her husband were, than he declared he would instantly go to her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "There have not, I believe, been many instances of a number of people met together, where every one was so perfectly happy as in this company.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000019_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000019_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "These were the charms which he could not bear to think his son had sacrificed to the daughter of Mrs Miller.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000021_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000021_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "Mr Western!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000021_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000021_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "He began, indeed, once to debate the matter, and assert his right to talk to his own daughter as he thought fit; but, as nobody seconded him, he was soon reduced to order.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000023_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000023_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "In confidence of this secrecy she went through the day pretty well, till the squire, who was now advanced into the second bottle, could contain his joy no longer, but, filling out a bumper, drank a health to the bride.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "These two, therefore, sat stoutly to it during the whole evening, and long after that happy hour which had surrendered the charming Sophia to the eager arms of her enraptured Jones.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "Thus, reader, we have at length brought our history to a conclusion, in which, to our great pleasure, though contrary, perhaps, to thy expectation, Mr Jones appears to be the happiest of all humankind; for what happiness this world affords equal to the possession of such a woman as Sophia, I sincerely own I have never yet discovered.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000027_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000027_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "He is also lately turned Methodist, in hopes of marrying a very rich widow of that sect, whose estate lies in that part of the kingdom.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3094_136458_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3094/136458/3094_136458_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3094",
        "content": "Square died soon after he writ the before mentioned letter; and as to Thwackum, he continues at his vicarage.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
